com.appiancorp.suiteapi.personalization

Class Operator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appiancorp.suiteapi.personalization.Operator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Operator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Holds the operator id and its display name. Operator id is required for searches. Default search operators include:
    • LIKE
    • EQUALS
    • GREATER_THAN
    • LESS_THAN
    • GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUALS
    • LESS_THAN_OR_EQUALS
    • DOES_NOT_EQUAL
    • CONTAINS
    • STARTS_WITH
    • ENDS_WITH

    Used in conjunction with GroupTypeService.getOperatorsForDataType(int)
    See Also:
    GroupTypeService, Serialized Form
